Diagnoses and Description of the World Genera of the Tribe Clivinematini (Heteroptera: Miridae)Taxonomic studies for 13 genera (Adlargidea Schaffner, 1890, Admetus Distant, 1883, Ambracius St√•l, 1860, Bothynotus Fieber, 1864, Clivinema Reuter, 1876, Clivinemidea Carvalho & Gomes, 1970, Froeschnerana Schaffner & Ferreira, 1989, Guanabarea Carvalho, 1948, Hemicerocoris Lethierry, 1881, Lamproscytus Reuter, 1907, Largidea Van Duzee, 1912, Megamiris Hsiao, 1947, Ofellus Distant, 1883) of the tribe Clivinematini are presented including description, diagnosis and list of synonymy for each. An adult habitus illustration of a representative species is provided for each genus, and a discussion of relationships for the genera of the world is given.